\b Executive Summary\b0\par
AI Resume Analyzer streamlines recruitment by parsing resumes, anonymizing PII, matching skills to job descriptions, and ranking candidates. It is a full-stack app with a React + Vite + TypeScript frontend and a Node.js + Express backend using MongoDB, Supabase auth, and Google Gemini for AI analysis.\par
